          View all services
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
          </svg>
        </a>
        <a
          href={`${base}/pricing`}
          class="inline-flex items-center text-zinc-900 font-medium hover:text-zinc-600 transition-colors"
        >
          View pricing
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Testimonial Section -->
    <section class="py-20">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <SectionDivider class="mb-12" />
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-zinc-900 mb-12">What Clients Say</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <!-- Testimonial 1 - Brian Fidler -->
          <div class="bg-zinc-50 p-8 rounded-lg border border-zinc-200">
            <div class="mb-6">
              <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-zinc-300" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10h-9.983zm-14.017 0v-7.391c0-5.704 3.748-9.57 9-10.609l.996 2.151c-2.433.917-3.996 3.638-3.996 5.849h3.983v10h-9.983z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <p class="text-lg text-zinc-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
              "Working with Savelle wasn't like working with a typical designer - it felt more like having a co-founder who just happened to be insanely talented at UX. When we were drowning in the complexity of 11 RV dealership locations and needed customers to actually find what they were looking for, Savelle didn't just design a filter system. He got in the weeds with us, understood our sales team's pain points, and built something that made everyone's life easier. That's rare."
            </p>
            <div class="pt-6 border-t border-zinc-200">
              <p class="font-semibold text-zinc-900">Brian Fidler</p>
